程序包 projecttwo

类 GymManager

java.lang.Object
projecttwo.GymManager
public class GymManager extends Object
This class is for the running of a Gym. Given commands can either add, delete, or print a list of members Given commands can also add, delete, or print a list of classes for members
作者:
Kangwei Zhu, Michael Israel

    • GymManager

      public GymManager()
      Default constructor.

  • 方法详细资料

    • run

      public void run()
      The method is used when the gym starts for the day. It will handle all the command listed in the instruction.

    • A

      private void A(String[] cmdLine, int addType)
      This method will add a Member Object into the member Database.
      参数:
      cmdLine - The information(attributes) of a Member object.
      addType - 0 : Member Object 1: Family Object which extends Member Object -1: Premium Object with extends Family Object

    • R

      private void R(String[] cmdLine)
      The method is used when removing a member to the database.
      参数:
      cmdLine - Takes in dob and full name of a member

    • P

      private void P()
      The method is used when printing/displaying a list of members in database.

    • PC

      private void PC()
      The method is used to display the list of members in the database. Ordered by the county names and then the zip codes; that is, if the locations are in the same county, ordered by the zip codes.

    • PN

      private void PN()
      The method is used to display the list of members in the database. Ordered by the members’ last names and then first names; that is, if two members have the same last name, ordered by the first name.

    • PD

      private void PD()
      The method is used to display the list of members in the database ordered by the expiration dates. If two expiration dates are the same, their order doesn’t matter.

    • S

      private void S()
      The method is used to display the fitness class schedule. A fitness class shall include the fitness class name, instructor’s name, the time of the class, and the list of members who have already checked in today

    • LS

      private void LS()
      This method handle the command "LS", which is the command that load the fitness class schedule from a text file to the class schedule in the software system.

    • LM

      private void LM()
      This method handles "LM" command, which loads the historical member information from a text file to the member database.

    • PF

      private void PF()
      This method handles the command "PF", which is print the list of members with the next billing statement membership fees.

    • doDG

      private boolean doDG(FitnessClass fitnessClass, Member guest)
      This method is used when dropping a member's guest to a specific class
      参数:
      fitnessClass - The specific fitness class that the guest is going to be dropped.
      guest - The guest
      返回:
      True if successfully dropped, false otherwise.

    • doCG

      private boolean doCG(FitnessClass fitnessClass, Member member)
      This method is used when checking in a member's guest to a specific fitness class.
      参数:
      fitnessClass - The specific fitness class that the guest is going to be checked into.
      member - The member which bring his guest.
      返回:
      True if successfully added, otherwise false.

    • doCAndD

      private void doCAndD(String[] cmdLine, int mode)
      This method is used for sperating the string typed array command lines. Do the checks before checkin a member/guest / drop a member/guest and then dispatch it to the methods that do the check in/drop member/guest.
      参数:
      cmdLine - The cmdLine array which has the attribute of the member.
      mode - 0 : check in a member into a fitness Class. 1 : drop a member from a fitness Class. 2 : check in a guest into a fitness Class. 3 : drop a guest from fitness Class.

    • checkDB

      private boolean checkDB(Member member)
      check whether a member is already in database or not
      参数:
      member - The member that are going to be checked.
      返回:
      True if not exist, otherwise false.

    • isTimeConflict

      private boolean isTimeConflict(FitnessClass fitnessClass, Member member)
      Check if there is time conflict when a member want to check in a fitnessClass. That is, if the member has already registered a fitness class that the time of the fitnessClass he wants to check in. That is considered as time conflict.
      参数:
      fitnessClass - The fitness class that the mmember wants to check in.
      member - The member that are going to check in a class
      返回:
      True if there is time conflict, false otherwise.

    • doCheckIn

      private boolean doCheckIn(FitnessClass fitnessClass, Member member)
      This method is used when check in a member into a fitnessClass. It also does the checking before add the member into the fitnessClass's student list.
      参数:
      fitnessClass - The fitness class this member wants to check in
      member - The member that are going to be checked in
      返回:
      True if successfully checked in, false otherwise.

    • isValidLocation

      private boolean isValidLocation(String loc)
      The method is used to see if a fitness class located at a location.
      参数:
      loc - The location of a fitness class
      返回:
      true if there is a fitness class located at the location. false otherwise

    • testCheckIn

      public boolean testCheckIn(FitnessClass fitnessClass, Member member)
      This method is used only for the junit test: check in before add member.
      参数:
      fitnessClass - The fitness class that the member is gonna checked in
      member - The member object that will check into one fitness class
      返回:
      True if successfully checked in, otherwise false.

    • testGuestCheckIn

      public boolean testGuestCheckIn(FitnessClass fitnessClass, Member member)
      This method is used only for the junit test: check in before add guest.
      参数:
      fitnessClass - The fitness class that the member's guest is gonna checked in
      member - The member's guest that will check into one fitness class
      返回:
      True if successfully checked in, otherwise false.

    • addSampleClassSchedule

      public void addSampleClassSchedule(FitnessClass[] fitnessClasses, int numOfClass)
      This method is used only for the junit test: add member.
      参数:
      fitnessClasses - The sample class schedule. Which is the array that holds all the fitness classes in this fitness chain.
      numOfClass - The number of fitness Class this fitness chain has.

    • readFiles

      private String[] readFiles(String fileName)
      This method is used when reading lines from text file.
      参数:
      fileName - The name of file
      返回:
      The String array that contains all the lines. Each element in this array is the one line in the text file.
